%H A038331 Bjorg N. Cyvin, Jon Brunvoll, and Sven J. Cyvin, <a href="https://match.pmf.kg.ac.rs/electronic_versions/Match34/match34_109-121.pdf">Isomer enumeration of unbranched catacondensed polygonal systems with pentagons and heptagons</a>, Match, No. 34 (Oct 1996), 109-121.
%H A038331 Bulat Khaidarov, <a href="https://cs.uwaterloo.ca/journals/JIS/VOL29/Khaidarov/khai3.html">Enumeration of Certain k-Block Partitions of Barry</a>, J. Int. Seq. 29 (2026), Art. 26.2.8. See p. 6 (Table 2).
%t A038331 Table[Binomial[i, j]*12^(i - j)* 5^j, {i, 0, 10}, {j, 0, i}] // Flatten (* _Michael De Vlieger_, May 22 2026 *)
%o A038331 (Python)
%o A038331 from sympy import binomial
%o A038331 def T(i, j): return binomial(i, j)*12**(i-j)*5**j
%o A038331 print([T(i, j) for i in range(8) for j in range(i+1)]) # _Michael S. Branicky_, Dec 05 2021
